{
  "stem": "20848.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And soon after the Germans walk in, they took away our shop.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You see, we didn't have the shop much longer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We only had it for two or three more weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And already I-- and there was a terrible tension at home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they started taking men away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember that my father was always hiding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they were taking-- they used to come into houses and take the men away, and they never came back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Coming back to the shop, we had a man working for us in the shop who was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a Pole.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he taught me how to walk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was-- ever since I remember him, he was working for my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a friend from the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this man was a nice, good-looking, tall man, blond, with blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we didn't know till later on, till the Germans walked-- marched in that he was what they call a volksdeutsche.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was not really a Pole.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He had a German background.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he put on a swastika immediately.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were absolutely devastated, because we always thought of him as a friend.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was the man who taught me how to walk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Can you imagine how long he worked for us?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as soon as the Germans walked in, he put on a swastika armband, and that was the end of him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So what happened to the shop?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the Germans took-- took away the whole shop with the stock.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had beautiful stock, because we had a lovely shop, which was, you know-- like, people used to come and be measured.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my parents had a lot of tailors that would give up the work out.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
